1
00:00:04,166 --> 00:00:07,633
We already stress out with the research
and now the strange case.

2
00:00:11,833 --> 00:00:14,533
What do you think about Kriss's death?

3
00:00:15,166 --> 00:00:17,966
Who actually killed her?
It's really strange.

4
00:00:19,166 --> 00:00:20,466
It is scary.

5
00:00:20,833 --> 00:00:22,633
We're still in her resort.

6
00:00:23,466 --> 00:00:24,599
Will she haunt us?

7
00:00:25,866 --> 00:00:27,533
It's giving me chills.

8
00:00:28,433 --> 00:00:31,099
It's not that bad.
Don't be scared.

9
00:00:31,733 --> 00:00:35,766
We're lucky that Kriss's aunt asked us
to take care of the resort for now.

10
00:00:36,699 --> 00:00:38,733
And there's barely any quest right now.

11
00:00:39,633 --> 00:00:41,866
We do good for her this much.

12
00:00:42,966 --> 00:00:44,500
She won't haunt us.

13
00:00:44,633 --> 00:00:45,633
Trust me.

14
00:00:46,233 --> 00:00:47,533
It's driving me crazy.

15
00:00:48,166 --> 00:00:49,686
We just want to research about shaman.

16
00:00:50,366 --> 00:00:52,046
But met with the psychopath killer
instead.

17
00:00:53,333 --> 00:00:54,699
What is this? Horror film?

18
00:00:55,099 --> 00:00:56,466
You two can stay here.

19
00:00:57,199 --> 00:00:58,266
Imma get some fresh air.

20
00:00:59,133 --> 00:01:00,373
I'll ask Phupha for some trips.

21
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:06,400
Let's continue working.

22
00:01:19,766 --> 00:01:24,000
Here. This is where villagers take what
they grow or grab it from the forest to sell.

23
00:01:24,733 --> 00:01:29,199
You're lucky that you didn't come here
on the weekend. This place will be full.

24
00:01:29,199 --> 00:01:32,733
Because this is where people comes to
take a picture of the beautiful views.

25
00:01:32,733 --> 00:01:35,300
Especially the rainy season,
the water looks stunning.

26
00:01:36,133 --> 00:01:39,800
You're right. The forest got everything.

27
00:01:40,566 --> 00:01:44,733
Believe it or not, this is also
the source of moonlight power.

28
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:49,633
In full moon night, those who believes
will take a shower under the moonlight.

29
00:01:49,833 --> 00:01:54,633
For real, bro?! Imma take a shower outdoor tonight.
I wan to have some charm like the others.

30
00:01:54,633 --> 00:01:57,666
Calm down.
Tonight is the new moon night.

31
00:01:58,066 --> 00:02:00,466
There's only ignorance that perform
the ritual at that night.

32
00:02:00,766 --> 00:02:01,900
It's risky.

33
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,800
- Or you wanna try?
- Nah, I'm good.

34
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,466
Hello, Phupha.

35
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,133
What are doing here?
